ED_Title: Report of the International Residual Mechanism for Criminal Tribunals
ED_DecisionText: At its 19th plenary meeting, on 18 October 2023, the General Assembly took note of the report of the International Residual Mechanism for Criminal Tribunals. (Footnote: A/78/257)
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/78/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
